    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it! This car is in absolutely incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. It\u2019s been babied since day one, kept in a garage, and there isn't a single scratch or dent to be found. It drives like an absolute dream! If you're looking for something that's basically brand new, this is the one for you. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'm happy to chat!",
      "price": 43900.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
