    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute pride and joy. This car is in incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied it since day one, keeping it spotless and making sure every single detail is perfect. It drives like a total dream and is ready for its next big adventure. You\u2019ve really got to see this beauty in person to see how pristine it is. Drop me a message if you want to come by and take a look!",
