    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a peerless E92 M3 featuring the high-revving S65 4.0L V8 paired with a precise 6-speed manual gearbox. This 'slick-top' example offers superior structural rigidity and a reduced center of gravity. All critical preventative maintenance has been addressed: rod bearings were replaced with VAC-treated shells and ARP bolts, and both throttle actuators have been upgraded with uprated gears. The chassis is equipped with Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and sits on staggered 19-inch Style 359M Competition wheels wrapped in fresh Michelin Pilot Sport 4S tires. The engine bay is pristine, showing no signs of valve cover weeping or VANOS rattle. This is a mechanically transparent, turn-key performance machine for the serious driver.",
